headline: Why Uber (UBER) Stock Is Trading Up Today

headline: Safe Pro’s Artificial Intelligence Dataset Surpasses 36,000 Landmine Detections and 2 Million Analyzed Drone Images, Strengthening Military and Humanitarian Operations
summary: AVENTURA, Fla., October 06, 2025--Safe Pro Group Inc. (Nasdaq: SPAI) ("Safe Pro" or the "Company"), a leader in AI-powered security and situational awareness solutions, today announced that its artificial intelligence (AI) models and algorithms have detected more than 36,000 landmines and explosive objects after analyzing over 2,000,000 drone images covering 22,500 acres of the battlefields of Ukraine.
